            </ph> which supersedes AU-C section 500A, <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Audit
                    Evidence</i>, and amends the following AU-C sections: <unknown id="UUID-1911b3ac-218a-078f-9079-2004d1718a11_N661755007ded1" class="- topic/unknown ">AU-C Section 500</unknown>
         </p>
