                    <unknown id="UUID-1911b3ac-218a-078f-9079-2004d1718a11_N6617550089519" class="- topic/unknown ">AU-C Section 500</unknown>
         </p>
         <p outputclass="box" class="- topic/p ">This SAS is effective for audits of financial statements for periods
                ending on or after December 15, 2022. A link to the final SAS and other resources
