                    Estimates, Including Fair Value Accounting Estimates, and Related
                    Disclosures</i>, and amends the following AU-C sections: <unknown id="UUID-1911b3ac-218a-078f-9079-2004d1718a11_N661755008a96b" class="- topic/unknown ">AU-C Section 540</unknown>
            <unknown id="UUID-1911b3ac-218a-078f-9079-2004d1718a11_N661755008bf92" class="- topic/unknown ">AU-C Section 540</unknown>
         </p>
         <ul outputclass="ul bullet" class="- topic/ul ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <xref format="dita" class="- topic/xref " href="../../ps/ad_us_auditing_standards_aicpa_clarified/ad_section_200_299/ad_200/ad_200.dita#UUID-a1c92cf4-004a-695b-1157-7fba820cf9c3">Section 200</xref>
                  <unknown id="UUID-1911b3ac-218a-078f-9079-2004d1718a11_N661755008d430" class="- topic/unknown ">AU-C Section 200</unknown>
               </p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <xref format="dita" class="- topic/xref " href="../../ps/ad_us_auditing_standards_aicpa_clarified/ad_section_200_299/ad_230/ad_230.dita#UUID-fc30ae30-57b7-c665-6108-6a72311bb2be">Section 230</xref>
                  <unknown id="UUID-1911b3ac-218a-078f-9079-2004d1718a11_N661755008e84c" class="- topic/unknown ">AU-C Section 230</unknown>
               </p>
            </li>
