         <p outputclass="box" class="- topic/p ">
            <xref format="dita" class="- topic/xref " href="../../ps/ad_us_auditing_standards_aicpa_clarified/ad_section_500_599/ad_540/ad_540.dita#UUID-5e295753-fd8e-ad8d-74c0-3d4d49ef0274">SAS No. 143</xref> addresses the auditor’s responsibilities relating to
